<br>
<br>
We're actively looking for  <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">WIZARDS</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END-->, <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">Necromancers</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END-->, <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">Clerics</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END-->, <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">Bards</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END-->, <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">Beastlords</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--><br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Requirements</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
- To be considered you must be 65 with a number of atleast 50 AA's. <br>
<br>
- You must atleast have a broadband connection.<br>
<br>
- Your character must atleast be elemental flagged or close to it to be considered.<br>
 <br>
- Prospects and members are expected to be active every day.<br>
<br>
- To apply, ask a friend in the guild to post you, in this post you should include your current level/AA with a magelos profile. You also need to specify your computer system and connection, any additional information is accepted, especially with cross-server applicants, which should include all previous guilds.<br>
<br>
- Any questions can be directed to Berton, Reynaldo or another officer if interested, leaving a post here is also accepted.<br>
<br>
<br>
These are our <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>AA requirements</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> by class:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Bard</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Required : Instrument Mastery 3, Singing Mastery 3, Epic, Combat Agility 3.<br>
Recommended: Harmonic Attack 5, Fading Memories, Lightning Reflexes 5, Combat Stability 3.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Beastlord</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Required : Spell Casting Reinforcement 3, Ambidex, Paragon, Improved Natural Durability 3, Mass Group Buff.<br>
Recommended: Beastial Frenzy 5.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Cleric</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Required : Casting Mastery 3, Unfailing Divinity 3,  Divine Arbitration 3, Mass Group Buff,.<br>
Recommended: Radiant Cure 3, Spell Casting Reinforcement, celestial regen<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Druid</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Required: Mass Group Buff, Casting Mastery 3, Radiant Cure 3.<br>
Recommended: Innate Camo, Exodus, Spirit of the Wood 3.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Enchanter</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Required: Dire Charm, Mass Group Buff, Casting Subtlety 3, Total Domintion 3.<br>
Recommended: Casting Mastery 3, Mental Clarity 3,Gather Mana.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Magician</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Required: Pet Discipline, Casting Mastery 3.<br>
Recommended: Mental Clarity 3, Quick Summoning.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Monk</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Required: Rapid Feign 3, Improved Natural Durability 3, Combat Agility 3<br>
Recommended: Lightning Reflexes 5, Critical Mend 3, Combat Stability 3 <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Necromancer</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Required: Lifeburn, Pet Discipline, Casting Mastery 3.<br>
Recommended: Dire Charm.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Paladin</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Required: Improved LoH, Natural Durability 3, Combat Agility 3, Combat Stability 3, Physical Enhancement, Planar Durability 3.<br>
Recommended: Lightning Reflexes 5, Innate Defense 5, Hand of Piety 3.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Ranger</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Required: Endless Quiver, Archery Mastery 3, Combat Fury 3, Combat Agility 3, Improved Natural Durability 3.<br>
Recommended: Fury of the ages 3, Lightning Reflexes 5, Combat Stability 3, Innate Camo.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Rogue</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Required: Escape,Natural Durability 3 ,Chaotic Stab, Combat Agility 3, Shroud of Stealth.<br>
Recommended: Ferocity 3, Lightning Reflexes 5.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Shadowknight</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Required: Improved Durability 3, Soul Abrasion 3, Combat Agility 3, Combat Stability 3, Planar Durability 3, Physical Enhancement.<br>
Recommended: Lighting reflexes 5, Innate Defense 5.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Shaman</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Required: Cannibalization, Mass Group Buff, Casting Mastery 3, Radiant Cure 3.<br>
Recommended: Improved Natural Durability 3.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Warrior</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
